      "text": "-Agents can take operational actions only within scope of the approved OAP \n- Strict Audit logs written to a common ledger\n- Strict COC, only COS can speak with planning agents, humans can initiate messages \n  but it is discouraged\n- Communicate A2A only within COC and stream, for incident common operating picture",
