    {
      "id": "KDTK48WIdBATu7P2ff7C3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2950.5633550534726,
      "y": 3599.5707579663353,
      "width": 1182.0513127776537,
      "height": 402.03548273810225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5z",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1265021766,
      "version": 3232,
      "versionNonce": 1548394061,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773802675722,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Initiating the Harness Design Summary\n\nUser needs access to capabilities within a harness - tool use, sub agents, write capabilities, skills etc.\nThe Personal Agent along with the user define a Scope of Work prepare context, and loop in human\ncollaborators as necessary. Once SOW is complete, User sets risk classification (which configures the\nsecurity of the harness) \n\nUser initiatives the project and launches the harness (the equivalent is launching Claude Code)\n\nPersonal agent gathers and prepares starting context for the new set of agents. \n\n** The nature of the project can scope up or down depending on complexity, you can have a short 1 min\nSOW, with one line IAP and a 10 minute Operational Period**\n",
      "fontSize": 22.973456156462984,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Initiating the Harness Design Summary\n\nUser needs access to capabilities within a harness - tool use, sub agents, write capabilities, skills etc. The Personal Agent along with the user define a Scope of Work prepare context, and loop in human collaborators as necessary. Once SOW is complete, User sets risk classification (which configures the security of the harness) \n\nUser initiatives the project and launches the harness (the equivalent is launching Claude Code)\n\nPersonal agent gathers and prepares starting context for the new set of agents. \n\n** The nature of the project can scope up or down depending on complexity, you can have a short 1 min SOW, with one line IAP and a 10 minute Operational Period**\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
