    {
      "id": "wkyvRMicGKHKa9G3J_GD3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 286.1269963513455,
      "y": 3393.3724503949848,
      "width": 975.0400390625,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6J",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 346520582,
      "version": 431,
      "versionNonce": 901975395,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773796363079,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Begins work in Git Repo with OAP Approval, the OAP is the first Commit of an Operational Period, ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Begins work in Git Repo with OAP Approval, the OAP is the first Commit of an Operational Period, ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "70JyJWX_KA6cnRK5ZZaZ6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 220.09999450116425,
      "y": 3619.84237921,
      "width": 1066.4272817273045,
      "height": 344.60184234694475,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6M",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 938107482,
      "version": 6802,
      "versionNonce": 962685187,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773796363079,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Operational Period\n\nThe OP should function largely autonomously managed by the Chief of Staff, who is the SPOC\nfor the human during the operational period. The work are bounded to the objectives\napproved in the OAP and managed via GitHub issues. \n\nSafe, scalable human in the loop governance is merged with autonomy by separating out\nstrategic work via tactical execution. Additionally, Operational Periods are time bound, meaning\nthat after a certain amount of time even if all objectives are not met, the work wraps up for\nhuman review, this can be based on either risk category (high risk shorter periods) or # of\nobjectives, low risk one or two objectives may be minutes. \n",
      "fontSize": 22.973456156462984,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Operational Period\n\nThe OP should function largely autonomously managed by the Chief of Staff, who is the SPOC for the human during the operational period. The work are bounded to the objectives approved in the OAP and managed via GitHub issues. \n\nSafe, scalable human in the loop governance is merged with autonomy by separating out strategic work via tactical execution. Additionally, Operational Periods are time bound, meaning that after a certain amount of time even if all objectives are not met, the work wraps up for human review, this can be based on either risk category (high risk shorter periods) or # of objectives, low risk one or two objectives may be minutes. \n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "XSfJ-sRRhCtohWJXriJMn",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -1721.0662334679578,
      "y": 319.5925527123562,
      "width": 1413.9650465873879,
      "height": 630.1092203985716,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
