      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "6fqFZumUqVkd8esjF7Cra",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1597.7184656534168,
      "y": 399.5291739774426,
      "width": 1179.4354658041837,
      "height": 467.9408187899339,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6O",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 883611590,
      "version": 340,
      "versionNonce": 2074113923,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773802445974,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Things to still look at \n\n- Communications Architecture \n- Skill Certification. \n- Agent Performance monitoring ",
      "fontSize": 74.87053100638944,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Things to still look at \n\n- Communications Architecture \n- Skill Certification. \n- Agent Performance monitoring ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "7mGVu0oCiWwKc47gulf1b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1356.775598890104,
      "y": 3618.081933501373,
      "width": 890.4333447716552,
      "height": 258.45138176020856,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6P",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 141509850,
      "version": 7359,
      "versionNonce": 1542672547,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773796363079,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Demobilization\n\nAt the end of each operational period there is mandated testing against OAP\nobjectives, as well as clear status reports, next steps, and code review\nreports. Once the User review and approves the AAR, all work is merged to\nmain and, if the next OAP is ready, the next OP can begin immediately\n\nAgents are measured for performance\n",
      "fontSize": 22.973456156462984,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Demobilization\n\nAt the end of each operational period there is mandated testing against OAP objectives, as well as clear status reports, next steps, and code review reports. Once the User review and approves the AAR, all work is merged to main and, if the next OAP is ready, the next OP can begin immediately\n\nAgents are measured for performance\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "iLzj1hALpIAtO3lNpWtrY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -96.43181748851703,
      "y": 276.0792496339958,
      "width": 1633.5741934010246,
      "height": 102.49299512788797,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6p",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 233241411,
      "version": 244,
      "versionNonce": 1230298541,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773802944722,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Human Authority — Humans command, agents execute. Every agent has a named\nhuman principal. Irreversible actions require explicit human authorization.",
      "fontSize": 40.99719805115519,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Human Authority — Humans command, agents execute. Every agent has a named human principal. Irreversible actions require explicit human authorization.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "SWXAjO2_UemZ7wS8bjEl5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -89.98888090466198,
      "y": 430.95495128207165,
      "width": 1600.6944856048651,
      "height": 102.49299512788797,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6q",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 646748899,
      "version": 300,
      "versionNonce": 1067884557,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773802944722,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Command Authority — Unity of command (one supervisor per agent). Chain of\ncommand is directional: assignments down, status up. No level-skipping.",
      "fontSize": 40.99719805115519,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Command Authority — Unity of command (one supervisor per agent). Chain of command is directional: assignments down, status up. No level-skipping.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "te4dymoFcleXS5lqqjPlv",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -85.77317314261882,
      "y": 586.3304987958594,
      "width": 1610.2878149352132,
      "height": 153.73949269183194,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6r",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1151157891,
      "version": 267,
      "versionNonce": 1599149677,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773802944722,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3. Management by Objectives — Every agent has a specific, assessable\nobjective per period. No freelancing — report out-of-scope findings, don't act\non them.",
      "fontSize": 40.99719805115519,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. Management by Objectives — Every agent has a specific, assessable objective per period. No freelancing — report out-of-scope findings, don't act on them.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
