      "text": "Key Bundles\ngranted based on\nprofile",
      "fontSize": 26.932914270313066,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Key Bundles granted based on profile",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "CaCePMCrYI5q5vb03awQO",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4470.07850403236,
      "y": 5201.096015164497,
      "width": 823.6564918199336,
      "height": 235.29513121678974,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b7t",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 141329059,
      "version": 1373,
      "versionNonce": 1072577955,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773796363079,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Three components:\n\n1. Registry — source of truth for what profile an agent has\n2. Key distribution — translates profile into a concrete bundle\nof keys and credentials\n3. Enforcement points — transport layer (orchestrator operations) +\nexternal systems (GitHub, APIs) that check for valid",
      "fontSize": 26.890872139061685,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Three components:\n\n1. Registry — source of truth for what profile an agent has\n2. Key distribution — translates profile into a concrete bundle of keys and credentials\n3. Enforcement points — transport layer (orchestrator operations) + external systems (GitHub, APIs) that check for valid",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rLvZn6VFpTH0p5ZvIGnDy",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4472.552421784351,
      "y": 4675.349295451277,
      "width": 402.8320843926969,
      "height": 137.31095316393993,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b7u",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1686940941,
      "version": 411,
      "versionNonce": 1866240323,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773796363079,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Transport encryption — hard\nguarantee, agent's keys\ndetermine what the network\naccepts",
      "fontSize": 27.462190632787983,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Transport encryption — hard guarantee, agent's keys determine what the network accepts",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "nG-8BrIXmtmGgjw0P8kse",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4474.429333957828,
      "y": 4969.0833839166935,
      "width": 403.6889084218876,
      "height": 137.37521189022905,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
