      "originalText": "Scope of Work\n\nRequired fields:\n- Project title\n- Objective (can be one line)\n- Project ID (unique)\n\nOptional fields:\n- Collaborator IDs (grants access to the project container)\n- Context (links, files, CLI commands to move data into the project)",
