      "updated": 1773967279047,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Project Container created:\n \n- Git repo (version history, file structure, access\ncontrol)\n- Redis project object (project ID, risk tier,\nstatus, assigned agents, active period)\n- Project-scoped encryption keys (the key bundle)\n- Project communication channels\n",
      "fontSize": 27.78737385005249,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Project Container created:\n \n- Git repo (version history, file structure, access control)\n- Redis project object (project ID, risk tier, status, assigned agents, active period)\n- Project-scoped encryption keys (the key bundle)\n- Project communication channels\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
