      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773972607462,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Orchestrator Spawns COS\n2. COS Checks in, Gets Keys\n\n3. COS Orients, asks questions of Planning Agent / Human\n\n4. COS Creates Issues from OAP and adds operational details \n(additional schema fields)\n\n5. COS Spawns Crew, each checks in, COS / supervisor validates understanding  \n6.  COS transitions to Execute, Notifes Human ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Orchestrator Spawns COS\n2. COS Checks in, Gets Keys\n\n3. COS Orients, asks questions of Planning Agent / Human\n\n4. COS Creates Issues from OAP and adds operational details \n(additional schema fields)\n\n5. COS Spawns Crew, each checks in, COS / supervisor validates understanding  \n6.  COS transitions to Execute, Notifes Human ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
